{"tid":2393533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府：學校之所以未能復課 係因為教師不願定期檢測","createTime":"2021-02-03T13:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T15:27:49.000Z","uid":191474,"like":5,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"a5775731b4e66259d7e1cdbcd911a78dbbff2b40","tid":2393533,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zb8HFUR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzb8HFUR.jpg&h=c1858d26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n學校相關既群組根本從未出現過<br />\n定期驗毒亦係拎避孕棒取代condom來避孕既思路<br />\n完全係零科學根據既做法<br />\n不過呢度先不討論定期檢測既logistics <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府依家拋個波俾校方<br />\n叫校方二揀一<br />\neither 強制學校教職員強制定期驗毒<br />\nor 承受不能復課既輿論壓力<br />\n<br />\n第一步 強迫教職員定期驗毒<br />\n第二步 強迫復課嘅學生定期驗毒<br />\n（已經可以拎晒全港學生嘅DNA）<br />\n第三步 可以牽涉到其他行業了"},{"pid":"cfa97629aec433684a67a358c9707f621d4f52a6","tid":2393533,"uid":191474,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:39:09.000Z","msg":"蘋果link<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/AFEU3PKF4ZF23BRW6EBQPKCVLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FAFEU3PKF4ZF23BRW6EBQPKCVLY%2F&d=f02Xtm2mX5FaAGCExHUdjRyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=985f5004\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FAFEU3PKF4ZF23BRW6EBQPKCVLY%2F&h=a4a6926e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/AFEU3PKF4ZF23BRW6EBQPKCVLY/</a>"},{"pid":"5178aae00e83f040c9e2b0bfda25dfbea7a616cc","tid":2393533,"uid":325346,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:50:27.000Z","msg":"同病毒講好數，校工,學生唔會播毒"},{"pid":"013250580dea20cc020c5e6c899405452a106ea9","tid":2393533,"uid":15835,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T13:51:41.000Z","msg":"過咗成年，教育局無乜收緊過政策 <br />\n學校會用好多原因叫啲家長帶仔女返學<br />\n升班出席率、學業、社交、搵社工、向教育局呈報&hellip;<br />\n但老師唔會敢講「你仔女返學係安全」<br />\n大家